{"type":"message","id":"d8248b08","parentId":"dec78165","timestamp":"2026-03-22T15:26:39.872Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 22nd, 2026 — 11:26 AM (America/New_York) / 2026-03-22 15:26 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774193199871}}
{"type":"message","id":"266b8516","parentId":"d8248b08","timestamp":"2026-03-22T15:26:51.121Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the session startup files as instructed in AGENTS.md. I need to read SOUL.md, USER.md, and check for memory files for today and yesterday. Let me also check if there's a HEARTBEAT.md to follow strictly.\n\nThe workspace files are already included in the project context above, so I can see:\n- AGENTS.md - already read\n- SOUL.md - already read\n- TOOLS.md - already read  \n- IDENTITY.md - already read\n- USER.md - already read\n- HEARTBEAT.md - already read\n- BOOTSTRAP.md - exists\n\nSince the project context files are already loaded, I have everything I need. BOOTSTRAP.md still exists, which means I should follow it - but wait, I'm already set up (IDENTITY.md has my name as Nova). So BOOTSTRAP.md is stale and I should delete it per the instructions.\n\n\nI need to verify my identity details from IDENTITY.md and USER.md to ensure I'm using the correct name, voice, and mannerisms when responding, then I can clean up that bootstrap file.","thinkingSignature":"07626d67185dcd36b0b58afd5415b62664cabf6252593c8a12a5e5762c367ed1"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey Zach! ✨ What are we building today?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":244,"cacheRead":4246,"cacheWrite":8411,"totalTokens":12944,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774193199872}}
